    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "elNrU2WOXHZLUzSxnKHVb/zbIh6Tf3O2pUyRyuwmQl0=",
    "originContent": "#### 🔥🔥🔥使用MyBatisPlus的方式，优雅的操作MongoDB",
    "translatedContent": "#### 🔥🔥🔥MyBatisPlus 방식을 사용하여 우아하게 MongoDB 조작하기"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "bBefIeb2K2KQVdirQPRU7QLki2hWORNHO4V9NjjiOyg=",
    "originContent": "  ",
